It all starts with hello.





We are committed to being investment advisors that you can trust.

Founded in 1987, and managing approximately $700 million (as of July 2015), Davidson & Garrard's professionals have over 200 years of combined investment experience. D&G specializes in customized equity, fixed income and alternative asset portfolios for individuals and families, institutions and retirement plans. Davidson & Garrard, Inc. is registered with the S.E.C. as an Investment Advisor.




